data.title: German Lopez Profile and Activity - Page 117
data.meta_description: German wrote for Vox since it launched in 2014, with a focus on politics and policy, and became cohost of The Weeds in 2021. Previously, he worked at CityBeat, a local newspaper in Cincinnati, covering politics and policy at the local and state level.
